{"word":"G91 - ἀδικέω - adikéō - ad-ee-keh'-o - Hurt","slug":"G91","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδικέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>adikéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ad-ee-keh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hurt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - adikeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ad-ee-keh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G94\">G94</a>; to <i>be unjust</i>, that is, (actively) <i>do wrong</i> (morally, socially or physically): - hurt, injure, be an offender, be unjust, (do, suffer, take) wrong."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G92\">G92</a>, <a href=\"#/G93\">G93</a>, <a href=\"#/G94\">G94</a>"}]}